*** Update for April 2, 2020 ***


Lewiston Grab & Go Meals. Monday, 5-7pm.


South entrance of school.


Stay in your vehicle. Meals will be delivered to your vehicle.





*** Updated School Meal Program ***



*** Updated April2, 2020 ***


Lewiston Consolidated Schools COVID-19 Breakfast and Lunch Program


Free breakfast and lunch will be provided until school resumes or the 19-20 school year ends.


Free breakfast and Lunch will be provided for any child between the age of 1-18.


A parent or guardian must notify the school how many children you need meals for.


Once you have reported the number of children you need meals for, you will not have to call in again, simply show up on Mondays to pick up your meals.


5 daysâ worth of breakfast and lunch meals can be picked up every Monday at Lewiston Consolidated Schools from 5:00 PM -7:00 PM.


There is NO application process and EVERY child is eligible regardless of income.


If you know of anyone unable to pick up their meals on Monday evenings, please have them contact the school for assistance.


Questions, please call the school and leave a message at 402-865-4675 or e-mail crowland@lewistonschool.net


